---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="书籍 — 雕龙 DragonCraft" locale="zh">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>《叙事引擎》</h1>
    <p>AI时代的内容操作系统 · 22章完整方法论</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page-content">

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">第一部分：叙事方法论基础（引子 ~ C03）</h2>
      <div class="chapter-list">

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">引子</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">叙事平权</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">好叙事不是天赋，是每个人都能学会的底层能力。AI时代，这个能力比任何时候都更重要——也更容易被更多人掌握。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T130519==z--引子__intro__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C01</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">叙事本能：为什么人类生来就是讲故事的人</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">刷到一个视频，你划过去了。但听到一个故事，你会停下来，想听完——这就是叙事的原始力量。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201739==z--叙事本能__chapter01__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C02</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">八刀解剖法：如何精准评估一个叙事</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">历史、辩证、现象、语言、形式、存在、美感、元反思——八把刀，把任何叙事剖开，看清它的每一层结构。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T150835==z--八刀解剖法__chapter03__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C03</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">个人IP：把自己的经历变成资产</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">你以为个人IP是"讲经历"，实际上它是"设计经历"。同样一段经历，不同的讲法，效果天差地别。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T152339==z--个人IP__chapter04__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">第二部分：场景Skill（C04 ~ C14 + C20 + C22）</h2>
      <div class="chapter-list">

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C04</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">品牌叙事：让用户主动认同"你是谁"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">产品可以被复制，功能可以被超越，但品牌故事是买不走的资产——前提是你讲对了。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T152919==z--品牌叙事__chapter05__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C05</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">产品发布：让观众看完就想下单</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">另一场发布会看完了，关掉直播，立刻想下单——这背后不是产品，是叙事节奏的精确设计。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T153542==z--产品发布__chapter06__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C06</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">创业融资：让投资人相信"非你不可"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">BP里写的是市场规模和商业模式，投资人真正投的是"这个人讲的故事靠不靠谱"。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T153825==z--创业融资__chapter07__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C07</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">销售说服：让客户听完就说"我考虑一下"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">产品功能倒背如流，客户听完却说"我再考虑考虑"——你没有讲故事，你只是在报参数。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T190641==z--销售说服__chapter08__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C08</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">组织变革：让员工主动拥抱新战略</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">老板在台上讲得热血沸腾，员工坐在下面想的是"又要折腾了"——战略没问题，是讲法出了问题。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T191402==z--组织变革__chapter09__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C09</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">公益筹款：让捐赠者觉得"这件事跟我有关"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">每天有XX名儿童饿死——这种数字让人麻木。好的筹款叙事让人感觉：我的参与真的能改变什么。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T193857==z--公益筹款__chapter10__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C10</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">社交媒体：3秒钩子+45秒展开+金句收尾</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">写了一篇干货文章，发出去阅读量300。写了一篇故事，阅读量30000——区别不在内容，在结构。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T194441==z--社交媒体__chapter11__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C11</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">教育开场：3分钟拉入学习状态</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">学员脑子里装的是工作、报表、晚饭吃什么。好的开场叙事，能在3分钟内把他们的注意力拽进另一个世界。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201918==z--教育开场__chapter12__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C12</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">公关危机：4A模型把"事故"变成"故事"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">舆情在发酵，老板在催，法务在拦，公关在想怎么发声明——4A模型让危机叙事有路可走。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201918==z--公关危机__chapter13__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C13</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">探索式叙事：让用户自己发现彩蛋</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">直接告诉用户"我们产品好"，用户直接划走。自己探索出来的结论，信任度是接收告诉的3倍。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201918==z--探索式叙事__chapter14__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C14</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">开源项目叙事：让代码讲出自己的故事</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">好代码只是门槛，让项目真正被使用的是叙事——README的三行与三百行，差别不在字数，在有没有回答"为什么是你"。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--开源项目叙事__chapter20__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C15</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">叙事领导力：让改变从"我"变成"我们"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">为什么有人能推动改变，有人不能？区别不在权力，在于有没有能力讲出一个让人愿意追随的故事。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--叙事领导力__chapter22__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">第三部分：AI时代叙事进阶（C16 ~ C21）</h2>
      <div class="chapter-list">

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C16</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">元Skill：把叙事方法变成AI可执行的指令</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">你脑子里的叙事方法，AI听不懂。把方法转译成Prompt，是AI时代叙事者的核心竞争力。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--元Skill__chapter15__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C17</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">叙事记忆库：构建你的叙事资产</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">灵感不记录就会消失。把散落的思考、案例、金句，变成可检索、可复用的叙事资产。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--叙事记忆库__chapter16__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C18</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">去AI化：让AI辅助的叙事依然有"人味"</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">AI写的总是"差不多"——去AI化，是在AI生成的底稿上保留那些只有人才能创造的真实细节和情感。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--去AI化__chapter17__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C19</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">人机协作工作流：从碎片到发布</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">idea→AI初稿→人工提炼→发布迭代——一套可复用的工作流，让AI成为叙事者的放大器而不是替代品。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--人机协作工作流__chapter18__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C20</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">个人IP：把简历变成故事</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">打开你的LinkedIn或公众号介绍，你写的是"XX公司创始人"还是"我为什么做了这件事"？前者是简历，后者是故事。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--个人IP__chapter19__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter-item">
          <div class="chapter-main">
            <span class="chapter-num">C21</span>
            <div class="chapter-body">
              <div class="chapter-title">叙事技能的持续进化</div>
              <div class="chapter-desc">叙事能力不是学一次就够了——是一套持续迭代的系统。从刻意练习到直觉内化，通向叙事自由的路径。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chapter-versions">
            <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--叙事技能的持续进化__chapter21__book.org" target="_blank" class="chapter-link">书籍版 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section note">
      <p>📌 章节源文件托管于 GitHub，GitHub 原生支持 .org 格式渲染。完整书籍版可从 GitHub 阅读或下载。</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .chapter-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .chapter-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: white;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .chapter-item:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .chapter-main { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; flex: 1; }
  .chapter-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    min-width: 50px;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .chapter-body { flex: 1; }
  .chapter-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .chapter-desc { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .chapter-versions { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .chapter-link {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 3px 12px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .chapter-link:hover { background: var(--accent); color: white; }
  .note {
    background: rgba(192,57,43,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.15);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .chapter-item { flex-direction: column; }
    .chapter-versions { align-self: flex-end; }
  }
</style>
